reviewText: Very good course material and very interesting
The materials are quite up-to-date, with a nice flow, and really interesting guest speakers. Thank you and treasure the learning!

For my country this course gives a perspective on the future because it seems that at the moment nobody thinks about sustainable business models. I hope I'm mistaken. So thank you for such marvellous course. It was pleasure to watch and learn!
Es war ein sehr guter Kurs, der viel Spaß beim Lernen gemacht hat und besonders praxisorientiert aufgebaut ist. Herzlichen Dank!

Very good! Should update some of the businesses f.ex. Too Good ToGo, and also include servicebusinesses, not only products for producing and selling. And maybe give us not english as first language some extras (Smile) Very good digital portal!
